	<div itemprop="text"><p>The main issue I&#8217;m seeing on various packages is the limited amount of bandwidth. 50GB is not a bad estimate for average usage, but I don&#8217;t want to suddenly get presented with an epic bill for bandwidth if I&#8217;m suddenly slashdotted or something.</p>
