	<div itemprop="text"><p>The 500 errors I&#8217;m seeing are on a single WP install with its own user. I noticed it at first on a WP install with what turned out to be a busy plugin. But subsequently I&#8217;m having issues on simple WP installs with only a couple of basic plugins running. If you want to know more: <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/topic/500-internal-server-errors-with-dreamhost?replies=22" rel="nofollow">http://wordpress.org/support/topic/500-internal-server-errors-with-dreamhost?replies=22</a></p>
